# 📊 Adherence Dashboard

## 🎯 Objective
Track real-time agent and supervisor adherence using IEX data provided by Real Time Analysts.

## 📈 KPIs & Visuals
- Adherence % by agent, team, and supervisor
- Auxiliary states visualization
- Proactive adherence scorecard

## 🛠 Tools & Techniques
- Power BI (slicers, bookmarks, DAX)
- IEX data integration (minutes format)
- Visualization breakdowns by hierarchy

## 💡 Highlights
- Designed for real-time coaching and performance optimization
- Replaces manual spreadsheets
- Quick identification of non-adherence trends

